I Like to Play Games;;1995;;R;;Drama;;5.1;;Robert Kubilos;;Lisa Boyle,Ken Steadman,James DiZazzo,Pamela Dickerson,Toshiya Agata,Tom Druzbick,Jennifer Burton,Monique Noel,Brittney Kwon,Cappuccino Moore,Cheryl Rixon,Kenneth Roussell,Eddie Hargitay;;Michael can't find a woman who'll play the sexual games that turn him on until gorgeous Suzanne lands a job in his office. Their business quickly turns into pleasure as she becomes everything he desires. From innocent schoolgirl to dominant seductress her games become twisted as their passions escalate into a game of life and death.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0113368/